description:
In this course, you will learn how to master Writing & Language section of the SAT. This course is for you if you usually pick an answer based on "what sounds right."

Learn how to pick an answer based on

  1. Connected meaning - pick an answer that connects with the sentences around it.
  2. Grammar - learn the main grammar rules that are tested.
  3. Style - discover what the College Board considers to be 'good' style.

After taking this course, you should practice these skills with the Official SAT Study guide to see results.
title: New SAT Writing 800: Guaranteed Results
